data.description: Welcome to the gated community of Bridgegate! This over sized two story home with the master and secondary bedrooms and bathrooms downstairs. The master includes a jacuzzi tub with a separate shower and spacious walk in closet. Upstairs is the perfect entertaining spot with a large loft and a den, as well another secondary bedroom and full bath. Enjoy the large peaceful backyard in this pool size lot! The Bridgegate community is a gated area in the community of Canyon Hills. Canyon Hills offers multiple pools, parks and schools close by!       Professional pictures coming soon!
